Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by Jessie Wiseman and special guest host SERE Specialist Tiffany Hart bring you the realest fake news of the week including Jon Stewart testifying before Congress for the 9/11 first responders health care bill, Nevada banning pre-employment marijuana tests, the US Women's soccer team stomping Thailand, the dodgeball debate in Vancouver, and the company that will name your baby for $350.
